<p>He released his first solo album Song Painter in 1970, with his breakthrough album coming in 1972 with Baby, Don't Get Hooked On Me.</p>

<p>The album was certified platinum, along with his 1974 album Stop and Smell the Roses.</p>

<p>Davis was named the Academy of Country Music's Entertainer of the Year award in 1974. </p>

